&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;Scripture&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Therefore said some of the Pharisees, &lt;strong&gt; This man is not of God, because he keepeth not the sabbath day. &lt;/strong&gt; Others said, How can a man that is a sinner do such miracles? And there was a division among them.&lt;/p&gt;
