&lt;p&gt;&lt;sup&gt;11&lt;/sup&gt; For with stammering lips and another tongue will he speak to this people.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;sup&gt;12&lt;/sup&gt; To whom he said, &lt;strong&gt; This is the rest wherewith ye may cause the weary to rest; and this is the refreshing: yet they would not hear. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;sup&gt;13&lt;/sup&gt; But the word of the LORD was unto them precept upon precept, precept upon precept; line upon line, line upon line; here a little, and there a little; that they might go, and fall backward, and be broken, and snared, and taken&lt;/p&gt;
