&lt;div class=&quot;Scripture&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;sup&gt;28&lt;/sup&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ScriptureChristRED&quot;&gt; Come unto me, all ye that labour and are heavy laden, and &lt;strong&gt; I will give you rest &lt;/strong&gt; . &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;sup&gt;29&lt;/sup&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;ScriptureChristRED&quot;&gt; Take my yoke upon you, and learn of me; for I am meek and lowly in heart: and &lt;strong&gt; ye shall find rest unto your souls &lt;/strong&gt; . &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
